	   <tr><td colspan=2>isn't the formula for mana int/5 then multiplied with your lvl? so 5(int)/5=1&nbsp;&nbsp;1x50(lvl) is 50<br>so if u think about it 50/5 is 10 mana per int/wis... not 100% sure but i'd say 95% <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
